        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p>Hello {first_name, \"there\"},</p><p>Welcome to 2021, and for the UK residents amongst you, back into lockdown.</p><p>I took some time away from the internet over Christmas, and am working through my backlog of work, emails and articles, when I'm not homeschooling my daughters. I'll be taking the best of those articles and doing these short digests of “catch-up” reading every few days, exclusively for members of the site.</p><p>Let me know what you think.</p>"
      },
